[The outbreak in 2006 was reported by ProMED-mail (see references below).

In 2010, Nepal reported 3335 malaria positive blood films, 575 diagnosed with _P. falciparum_ and 1706 with _P. vivax_. There were 129 hospital admissions and 8 deaths (World Malaria Report 2010). - Mod.EP

A HealthMap/ProMED-mail map can be accessed at: http://healthmap.org/r/1COd.]
